name: fake-user-agent
readme:
fake-user-agent
==========

```
npm install fake-user-agent
```

```
var agents = require('fake-user-agent');

var headers =  {
  "User-Agent": agents.IPHONE_IOS5
};
```

Used for fake the client user agent.
